Class LoggerLog4j

java.lang.Object
org.apache.logging.log4j.spi.AbstractLogger
com.dua3.utility.logging.backend.log4j.LoggerLog4j
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, org.apache.logging.log4j.Logger, org.apache.logging.log4j.spi.ExtendedLogger, org.apache.logging.log4j.spi.LocationAwareLogger
public class LoggerLog4j extends org.apache.logging.log4j.spi.AbstractLogger
LoggerLog4j is an implementation of the Log4J AbstractLogger class that forwards all logging calls to the global UniversalDispatcher instance.
